dataIdInfo.idPurp: Property ownership information from Certificates of Title registered at Alberta Land Titles.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: Ownership information for all properties with a Certificate of Title registered at Alberta Land Titles, and found within the Regional Municipality of Wood Buffalo. The titled owners table is comprised of two parts; a unique LINC value that corresponds to the geographic extent of a property and the property ownership information obtained from registered title. The LINC number is the descriptor for each title associated with a property. A distinct property may have more than 1 Title or more than 1 owner. The Titled Owners table is associated with the cadastral information that is acquired from AltaLIS and is updated on an on-going basis.

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.
